Package net.swofty.redisapi.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ChannelAlreadyRegisteredException  
    ChannelDefinitionError
    This class is a custom exception that is thrown when a channel definition is invalid, this is usually because there is no event consumer or class passed through
    ChannelNotRegisteredException
    This class is a custom exception class that is thrown when a class is not registered yet there is a message trying to be sent through it
    CouldNotConnectToRedisException
    This class is a custom exception class that throws when jedis process is unable to connect to Redis
